headline: The Bull Case For Weyerhaeuser (WY) Could Change Following Earnings Surge and Portfolio Shifts—Learn Why
summary: Weyerhaeuser Company recently reported third-quarter 2025 results, posting net income of US$80 million compared to US$28 million a year prior, alongside basic and diluted earnings per share of US$0.11, up from US$0.04 in the same period last year.
